        <div class="span-two-thirds">
            <div class="page-header">
                <h1>
                    Setting up Jaggery
                </h1>
            </div>

            <ol>
                <li>Extract <code>jaggery-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT_M4.zip</code></li>
                <li>The bin folder will contain all the Jaggery execution scripts.</li>
                <li>Run <code>sh bin/wso2server.sh (bin/wso2server.bat)</code> command to start the server.</li>
            </ol>

        </div>
        <div class="span-one-third">
            <p align="right">
                <a class="btn success large" href="http://dist.wso2.org/products/jaggery/dl/jaggery-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT_M4.zip">Download Jaggery (M4) </a>
            </p>
        </div>
